831439\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Additional Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Online Multiplayer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Detritus features Online Multiplayer, with an always available server. Simply create a game and toggle the 'Online' setting to make your lobby Live!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>2 - 8 Players</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the lobby host, you can toggle the max number of players for your game. All players which aren't human will be replaced by the brutal &amp; relentless CPUs who will ensure your destruction. Up to 8 players are available per lobby, offline &amp; online, with the exception of Turn Based which supports 4 Teams</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Controller Support</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keyboard controls can of course be mapped to keys of your choice, but Detritus also features Controller Support!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>This game is being constantly developed, stay tuned for updates!</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["AJ Studio"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387050/header.jpg?t=1737831439","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":false,"id":257078629,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257078629/movie480.mp4?t=1733489848","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257078629/movie_max.mp4?t=1733489848"},"name":"Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257078629/78426065d843e9b4c98fc55b3935403d3f102015/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1733489848","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com